一來淆底，二來驚有手尾(雖然我知唔切都會有手尾)。<br />\n<br />\n依家食緊中藥，唔知好唔好到。唔得就要十月同西醫講切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9e506d7ba040f86d31abdcd561e18191478395","tid":358841,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吞根扁桃線肥大，成日搞到我有d 野頂住個喉嚨 <br />\n做手術既話可唔可以好返？ 同埋會唔會番發？？</blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n天氣一轉或者免疫力差病左嗰排會覺得左邊扁桃腺同喉嚨好漲，而且兩邊扁桃腺好腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我照超聲波仲見到d頸淋巴好多多腫起一粒粒，係良性，但撳落會痛。<br />\n<br />\n上個月西醫問我切唔切，我考慮緊。一來淆底，二來驚有手尾(雖然我知唔切都會有手尾)。<br />\n<br />\n依家食緊中藥，唔知好唔好到。唔得就要十月同西醫講切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5931ebc6d416867beaefe081650def456f974a94","tid":358841,"uid":23610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:09:05.000Z","msg":"舌根，sorry😷😷"},{"pid":"3aeb0bb5bcf88d7b8df5ee32f41585ceeb6c8d95","tid":358841,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n割"}]}